<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٥ - <span class="c2">(٢٢١٨)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2591">أَبُو الرَّبِيعِ سُلَيْمَانُ بْنُ دَاوُدَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">وَقُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ وَهُوَ ابْنُ زَيْدٍ </a>. <span class="c2">(ح)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3889">أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ - كِلَاهُمَا عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4822">عَمْرِو بْنِ دِينَارٍ </a>بِإِسْنَادِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ نَحْوَ حَدِيثِهِ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>